item.title: CBHS Yard Sign
item.description: Proud of your Cocoa Beach Senior? Let them know, order a yard sign!!! Form Simply download the form above and mail it completed along with the $20 fee to: Cocoa Beach Project Graduation PO Box 321577 Cocoa Beach, FL 32932-1577 Signs will be ordered as needed and will be available for purchase through the month of April. They will be delivered to the school and parents/students notified via email.
